title: Twisted Treeline
body: Is there a ranked 3v3 queue for twisted treeline yet? My friends and I were thinking of spamming that and trying to get a better division. Also if there is what day is it up.

replies.body:
There is no Ranked 3v3 at present.
Riot is using the old lame excuse of server pop blah blah blah, instead of making Thurdays Ranked 3v3 and Fri/sat Normal 3v3 they prefer to do nothing.
I don't think that there is one yet, however one of my friends seems to think that there is... so you never know.
